SUMMARY:Yoga Deconstructed
DTSTAMP:20260701T101452Z
DTSTART:20260726T133000Z
DESCRIPTION:Explore the fundamentals of yoga through a detailed breakdown o
	f common poses and alignment principles. Learn techniques to support joint
	 safety\, improve body awareness and enhance your practice with greater co
	nfidence and skill. Whether you’re new to yoga or looking to refine your p
	ractice\, this workshop offers valuable insights for all levels. \nRegistr
	ation link coming soon.\n\nhttps://www.erjcchouston.org/event/yoga-deconst
	ructed/\n\nFrom ERJCC Houston
URL:https://www.erjcchouston.org/event/yoga-deconstructed/
