DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the holiday of love with a workout designed for two! 
	Join Meryl and Adam for a fun-filled evening of partner exercises\, team c
	hallenges\, laughs and plenty of movement. No fitness experience required—
	just bring your sweetheart\, best friend or favorite workout partner and g
	et ready to sweat\, connect and have a great time together!\n\nhttps://www
	.erjcchouston.org/event/sweathearts-a-fitness-class-date-night-tu-bav-edit
