	our friends and family with open gym in the gymnastics center followed by 
	musical services. \nOpen gym will begin at 10:00 AM in the gymnastics cent
	er\, followed by music and services at 11:00 AM in the atrium of the Samue
	ls Family Community Pavilion. \nRSVPs are required and spaces are limited.
